accessories.title: Classy Bag
accessories.description: Your work-to-gym hybrid. The Everyday Holdall is specifically designed for your everyday items, with a wet pocket for gym kit and slip pockets for work essentials, as well as a main-entry space for anything else you need for the journey. Complete with super comfy padded carry handles and shoulder strap.

supplements.title: Whey Protein
supplements.description: Unleash the power of optimal nutrition with our Whey Protein Blend, the ultimate companion for your fitness journey. Crafted with precision and dedication, this premium whey protein powder is designed to elevate your workout experience and support your body's recovery.
supplements.description2: Packed with high-quality whey protein, each serving delivers a potent dose of essential amino acids, promoting muscle growth and repair. Whether you're a seasoned athlete or just starting your fitness adventure, our Whey Protein Blend is the ideal choice to fuel your body with the nutrients it craves.
